c%e8%a8%b4%2c528%2c20211118%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,訴,528,20211118,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"528","JDATE":"20211118","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}